                    >
                      üéâ Join Our Events
                    </a>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="md:col-6 mb-6">
                <h3 class="h4 mb-4">About Our Organization</h3>
                <ul class="space-y-3">
                  <li><strong>Status:</strong> 501(c)(3) Nonprofit</li>
                  <li><strong>EIN:</strong> 33-3432965</li>
                  <li><strong>UBI:</strong> 605 729 334</li>
                  <li><strong>Founded:</strong> February 2025</li>
                  <li><strong>State:</strong> Washington</li>
                </ul>

                <div class="mt-6">
                  <h4 class="h6 mb-2">Transparency & Accountability</h4>
                  <p class="text-sm mb-4">
                    We believe in complete transparency. All our official IRS
                    documents, board information, and organizational filings are
                    publicly available for your review.
                  </p>
                  <a
                    href="/documents"
                    class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-blue-600 text-white text-sm rounded hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors"
                  >
                    üìÑ View All Official Documents
                  </a>
                </div>

                <div class="mt-6">
                  <h4 class="h6 mb-2">Connect With Us</h4>
                  <p class="text-sm mb-4">
